                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9964" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">MKT-1487</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1905 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">连接-撬动-学习：H文具公司借道亚马逊平台的出海逆袭之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Linkage-Leverage-Learning: H Stationery Company&#39;s Overseas Market Counterattack Journey through Amazon</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">戴鑫，欧瑞榆，张佳龙，段邵楷，李艳丽，周二华</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">华中科技大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">H文具公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">贸易与金融业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中小型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">21 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">跨境电商；龙型跨国企业；LLL模型；国际营销；2025百优案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Cross-border E-commerce, Dragon Multinationals, LLL Model, International Marketing</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2015年，在政策市场的双轮驱动下，H文具公司从B端外贸公司转型为C端跨境电商，开启了国际市场开拓的道路。从2015年至2025年十年间，H文具公司借道亚马逊平台实现了出海逆袭之路，回答了跨境电商该“进入怎样的市场”、“如何进入市场”的关键问题。市场进入阶段，H文具公司依托亚马逊平台实现市场进入，初期产品A4纸产品的滞销让其认识到中美市场的差异。2016年，H文具公司依托成熟的B端供应商制造能力与选品经验，深耕细分市场文件夹品类得以立足。而后，越来越多中国品牌进入亚马逊平台，H文具公司卷入国内竞品价格战。2018年，H文具公司通过亚马逊平台规则学习、组织架构重塑，实现从精细化运营，在亚马逊第三方卖家中名列前三。市场突围后，H文具公司逐步将成功经验拓展到更多垂直品类上，随着细分市场饱和，再次遇到增量瓶颈。2022年，H文具公司基于亚马逊平台更新的算法机制，主动进行消费者行为研究，建立基于“产品-竞争-成本”三维度的选品策略以及“微创新”产品开发模式，在亚马逊平台上实现对海外竞争品牌的市场逆袭。H文具公司从缺乏市场认知到实现以用户需求为导向的产品“微创”，对跨境电商运营方式从陌生到创新，为我们展现了跨境电商企业在资源劣势条件下的出海逆袭之路。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">In 2015, H Stationery Company transformed from B2B foreign trade to B2C cross-border e-commerce, beginning its international expansion through Amazon. Over the 2015-2025 decade, the company achieved overseas market success by addressing key questions of market selection and entry strategies. Initially, poor sales of A4 paper products revealed significant differences between Chinese and American markets. In 2016, leveraging established B2B supplier relationships and product expertise, H Stationery established its market position by focusing on the file folder niche. As more Chinese sellers entered Amazon, H Stationery faced intense domestic price competition. By 2018, through mastering platform rules and organizational restructuring, the company achieved refined operations and ranked among Amazon&#39;s top three third-party sellers. After market breakthrough, H Stationery expanded to additional vertical categories but encountered growth bottlenecks as niche markets saturated. In 2022, responding to Amazon&#39;s algorithm updates, the company conducted consumer behavior research and developed a three-dimensional product selection strategy based on &quot;product-competition-cost&quot; dimensions, along with a &quot;micro-innovation&quot; development model. This enabled H Stationery to successfully compete against established overseas brands on Amazon. The company&#39;s evolution from limited market awareness to user-driven product innovation demonstrates how cross-border e-commerce enterprises can achieve overseas success despite resource constraints.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《营销管理》、《国际市场营销》、《跨境电子商务》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">龙型跨国公司；龙型跨国企业国际市场开拓过程的Linkage-Leverage-Learning(LLL)模型</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-10</td>
                            </tr>
